  "title": "Create API Key",
  "content": {
    "type": "procedural",
    "format": "markdown",
    "body": "Use a `curl` command to send a POST request to the `/api/v1/users/me/api-keys` endpoint to create a new API key. The request must include an Authorization Bearer Token, Content-Type as `application/json`, and JSON data containing the key name and scopes (e.g., `kb:read`, `kb:write`)."
